data.description: This beautiful home in Los Altos features an open floor plan with a large living area and a kitchen that looks out onto the sparkling pool. The kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless appliances, an abundance of cabinet space and an additional area that can be utilized as a workspace. A dual access fireplace opens to both the living and dining area. Both bathrooms have been upgraded with the hall bath having a jetted bathtub. The primary bedroom has sliding glass doors leading out to the backyard. The private backyard has a heated pool with patio area, a side yard with grass and fruit trees. Tesla solar panels, a 200-amp panel, a ring doorbell camera, hardwood flooring, recessed lighting, and central AC are just some of the great amenities of this Los Altos home. This home is move in ready and located near Prisk Elementary and Stanford Middle School.
